New Records: Jean-Philippe Krasso scored his third goal in these qualifiers
Key Match Events: Jean-Philippe Krasso scored the first goal in the 45th minute of injury time before the interval
Oumar Diakite scored the second goal 10 minutes into the second half
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match took place in Yaounde, Cameroon
Others: Ivory Coast is the reigning Afcon champions
Chad and Ivory Coast will face respective double-headers against Zambia and Sierra Leone respectively next month
